These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, water
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, reading
The people have 2 different jobs:  mechanic, fisherman
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: family, time-travel
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, r&b
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, basketball
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, jet-ski
1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking water is on the left of the mechanic##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Beverage      | water     | 7up |
| Hobby         | reading  | puzzles       |
| Job           | fisherman   | mechanic    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel     | family   |
| Music-Genre   | r&b      | ambient     |
| Sport         | basketball | sailing      |
| Transport     | jet-ski       | roller           |

