.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea
There 2 different types of food: lemon, raspberry
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, analyst
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, fantasy
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, australian
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, horse
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, snowmobile
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
3. the person watching fantasy movies is in an odd position##4
4. the australian is on the left of the accountant##1
5. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea         | 7up       |
| Food          | lemon        | raspberry |
| Job           | analyst | accountant    |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy        | mystery  |
| Nationality   | australian        | dutch       |
| Pet           | horse            | chinchilla        |
| Transport     | snowmobile            | quad-bike       |

