The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, basketball
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, train
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the owner of the pony is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
4. the bartender is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
5. the bartender is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
