.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, almond-milk
The people have 2 different hobbies: chess, magic-tricks
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, adventure
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: gospel, indie
2 different pets are kept: horse, hamster
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, badminton
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, car
1. the fan of gospel is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is badminton is in an even position##4
3. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's sport is badminton is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
6. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk    | hot-chocolate   |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | chess |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure      | martial-arts     |
| Music-Genre   | indie        | gospel        |
| Pet           | horse        | hamster |
| Sport         | snowboarding    | badminton |
| Transport     | car         | airplane       |

